<br>
And I guess I must have just been very lucky and have never seen a resist and I use it often.  The only time it's been resisted for me as I said was when the animal is too high, 47 and up.<br>
<br>
One interesting thing I had to test just to see what would happen, if you dispel your pet, you can dispel the Dire Charm.  So if it gets something nasty on it you would like dispelled, let it keep the nasties instead.<br>
<br>
The business about others not being able to buff or heal our pets really bugs me though.<br>
<br>
